---
import Tabs from "./Tabs";
import single from "../../assets/images/DrumMixers/baghouse.webp";
import LearnBtn from "../unitComponents/LearnBtn.astro";
import BagHousesOdometer from "./BagHousesOdometer";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<div class="w-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center font-bold">
  <div
    class="w-full flex flex-col mt-20 text-grisT max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 text-base md:text-xl"
  >
    <h1
      id="Baghouses"
      class="scroll-mt-20 text-2xl lg:text-4xl text-center lg:text-start md:text-start mb-10"
    >
      BAGHOUSES
    </h1>
    <div
      class="w-full grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-2 items-center"
    >
      <div>
        <p class="text-justify text-base lg:text-lg font-thin">
          A continuous cleaning system keeps the filter bags operating at all
          times. Compressed air pulses are released through a supersonic nozzle,
          creating a pressure wave that rapidly expands each bag and dislodges
          the dust layer from its surface. The released fine particles fall into
          the lower collector, where they are reintegrated into the production
          process.
        </p>
        <br />
        <p class="text-justify text-base lg:text-lg font-thin">
          Elimination of sludge pits and their costly operation.
        </p><br />

        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center rounded-lg space-y-5">
          <div class="flex flex-col">
            <div class="flex flex-row gap-2 items-center text-5xl font-medium">
              <p>4 - 90</p>
              <p class="font-medium text-sm">thousand ACFM</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="font-medium text-lg">Baghouses capacity</h2>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col">
            <div class="flex flex-row gap-2 items-center text-5xl font-medium">
              <p>99.99</p>
              <p class="font-medium text-sm">%</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="font-medium text-lg">
                Fine particle filtration efficiency
              </h2>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="w-full flex justify-center items-center pt-10 lg:pt-0 md:pt-0"
      >
        <Image src={single} alt="Attachable bag house" class="w-1/2" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div
    class="w-full flex flex-col items-center mt-20 text-grisT max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 text-base md:text-lg"
  >
    <Tabs client:visible />
  </div><br />
  <div class="w-full">
    <details class="group">
      <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none">
        <div
          class="w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto flex justify-between items-center px-8 py-6"
        >
          <h2
            class="font-bold text-grisT text-xl text-center lg:text-start md:text-start md:text-2xl"
          >
            Advantages of fines return system
          </h2>
          <svg
            class="transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180"
            width="64"
            height="64"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            ><g id="SVGRepo_bgCarrier" stroke-width="0"></g><g
              id="SVGRepo_tracerCarrier"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"></g><g id="SVGRepo_iconCarrier">
              <path
                d="M5.70711 9.71069C5.31658 10.1012 5.31658 10.7344 5.70711 11.1249L10.5993 16.0123C11.3805 16.7927 12.6463 16.7924 13.4271 16.0117L18.3174 11.1213C18.708 10.7308 18.708 10.0976 18.3174 9.70708C17.9269 9.31655 17.2937 9.31655 16.9032 9.70708L12.7176 13.8927C12.3271 14.2833 11.6939 14.2832 11.3034 13.8927L7.12132 9.71069C6.7308 9.32016 6.09763 9.32016 5.70711 9.71069Z"
                fill="#0F0F0F"></path>
            </g></svg
          >
        </div>
      </summary>

      <div class="w-full bg-grisT text-white py-10">
        <div
          class="w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 items-center"
        >
          <div class="w-full">
            <ul class="list-disc ml-6 font-thin text-sm md:text-base">
              <li>Improves the gradation of the hot-mix.</li>
              <li>Increases the density and cohesion of the final material.</li>
              <li>
                Reduces the consumption of virgin aggregates, optimizing
                production costs.
              </li>
              <li>
                Decreases environmental pollution by reincorporating captured
                dust.
              </li>
              <li>
                Contributes to a more uniform and durable mix with better
                structural properties.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="w-full">
            <h2
              class="text-base text-center mt-5 lg:mt-0 md:mt-0 lg:text-start md:text-start md:text-lg font-bold"
            >
              Mechanism of baghouses available in pulse jet and reverse jet
            </h2><br />
            <p class="font-thin">
              <span class="font-bold">Pulse Jet:</span>
              A cleaning system that uses compressed air bursts to dislodge dust and
              debris from the filter bags, maintaining continuous airflow.
            </p><br />
            <p class="font-thin">
              <span class="font-bold">Reverse Air:</span>
              A cleaning system that blows air in the opposite direction to remove
              dust from the filter bags, typically used in larger baghouses or high-dust
              applications.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </details>
  </div>

  <div
    class="w-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center mt-5 md:mt-20 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8"
  >
    <div>
      <video
        playsinline
        controls
        poster="/Gallery/customdes.webp"
        preload="metadata"
        width="1280"
        height="720"
      >
        <source src="/Videos/Webm/DMVideo.webp" type="video/webm" />
        <source src="/Videos/Mp4/DMVideo.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
      </video>
      <p class="font-thin text-center text-grisT">
        TriasoÂ® baghouses are portable, self-contained units that operate at
        air-to-cloth ratios up to 8:1
      </p>
    </div><br />
    <LearnBtn href="/BagHouses" />
  </div>
</div>
